V 0.6.1 - 2026.04.07

* Refactor: `textResult()`, `errorResult()`, `persistTiddler()` helpers in shared.js
* Refactor: hashline `HASH_SEP` constant, added space after colon in output
* MCP instructions: persistence warning when `listen` is not active

V 0.6.0 - 2026.04.07

* `inspect_tw`: auto-reduce depth when result exceeds 10K chars
* `run_filter`: show full titles instead of prefix-grouped tree
* `render_tiddler`: add `mode` parameter (raw / viewtemplate)
* `reload_tiddlers`: add `scope` parameter (tiddlers / shadows / all)
* `inspect_tw`: allow `$tw.utils.*` functions in call whitelist
* `inspect_tw`: auto-resolve path + call when path is an object
* New `render_field` tool for rendering individual fields / data indices

V 0.5.0 - 2026.04.02

* initial release
* name: tw-mcp server
